attributes.name: Cure Injoy 2G Bubblegum OG All in One Device
attributes.body: Bubble Gum OG has been winning cannabis awards since 1994, including countless Cannabis Cups. This strain features classic flavors of your favorite bubble gum with hints of cotton candy. With every hit, imagine your worries turning into playful bubbles, floating away into the carefree abyss.

attributes.name: Cure Injoy 2G Green Gusherz All in One Device
attributes.body: Green Gushers is a great daytime strain that can aid in fatigue and depression while giving you an uplifting high . Picture biting into a juicy green gummy and suddenly being transported to a psychedelic candy land where the rivers flow with limeade and the trees sprout sour apple lollipops.

attributes.name: Cure Injoy 2G Pineapple Punch All in One Device
attributes.body: Perfect for an afternoon rip before getting your grocery shopping done. the strain that hits you so hard with tropical vibes; even your taste buds will be doing the hula. Like a luau for your senses, every toke an invitation to a Pineapple Paradise Party.

attributes.name: Cure Injoy 2G Pink Panties All in One Device
attributes.body: Slip your taste buds into something a little more comfortable. With every inhale, imagine your senses cozying up in a pink cloud of juicy delight, and with every exhale your worries flutter away like lingerie in the wind. It's the kind of strain that makes you wonder if Cupid moonlights as a budtender, shooting arrows of relaxation straight to your heart.

attributes.name: Cure Injoy 2G Skywalker OG All in One Device
attributes.body: Skywalker OG is known for its relaxing and euphoric effects with flavor notes of earthiness and spice. It’s a strain that's so potent, it could turn Yoda into a giggling green Jedi. So, prepare for liftoff, because with this strain, you'll be reaching new heights, and your high will be soaring through the stars at warp speed. May the Dank Side be with you!

attributes.name: Cure Injoy 2G Strawnana All in One Device
attributes.body: A strain known for it’s high THC content, it will leave you feeling uplifted and creative. Every hit is like a tropical dance party in your mouth, where strawberries and bananas groove together in perfect harmony. It's the kind of strain that makes you want to put on a fruit hat and salsa your way to a stress-free paradise. Get ready to go bananas for Strawnana!

attributes.name: Cure Injoy 2G Tropical Gelato All in One Device
attributes.body: Tropical Gelato offers a unique combination of fruity flavors while relaxing your mind. Great for novice and seasoned cannabis consumers, it features flavors of sweet pineapple, vanilla and key lime pie. It's the kind of strain that transfers you to a flavor oasis, with each flavor swirl bringing you closer to a state of pure chillaxation.

attributes.name: Cure Injoy 2G Zkittles All in One Device
attributes.body: Zkittles is a unique cross between Grape Ape, Grapefruit and an undisclosed strain. As for it’s flavor, it’s exactly what you’d expect; candied cherries, orange soda and bright citrus. Taste the rainbow, embrace the high, and let Zkittles take you on a whimsical flavor adventure that's more magical than a unicorn's day off!

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Concord Cream
attributes.body: Concord Cream, a predominantly Indica strain, is the sweet sweet love child of Grape Bubba and Cookies & Cream. This soothing bud, rich in flavor, is a must-try for any grape strain fans. True to its name, Concord Cream boasts a super sweet and creamy fruity grape flavor complemented by notes of flowery violet and vanilla. The aroma mirrors this profile with a hint of sour grapefruit. Concord Cream is a favored choice for addressing various conditions across a whole spectrum, including stress, anxiety, muscle spasms, cramps, depression, and insomnia. The Concord Cream high unfolds gradually, initiating with a slow burn of euphoria that melts the mad/sad away. Concord Cream is wonderful for consumers that have social anxiety as its a very talkative, giggly strain! As the mental boost persists, a sense of physical relaxation takes over, eventually inducing a sleepy, sedative state.

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Chemmy Jones
attributes.body: Meet Chemmy Jones, a Sativa strain born from the genetic fusion of Chem D and Casey Jones. Offering an invigorating and refreshing encounter with a high THC content, Chemmy Jones brings forth a functional, high-energy buzz that fosters productivity. According to customer reviews, this strain is celebrated for its ability to promote energy, upliftment, and happiness. Its aroma and taste showcase diesel undertones harmonized with a floral sweetness.

attributes.name: Allsick - Wolf's Breath by Enchanted Botanicals
attributes.body: The Allsick Wolf's Breath, a collaborative creation by local legend Johnny James and Enchanted Botanicals, is a hybrid strain offering an experience thats ALL SICK. Its slight floral exhale, and tropical citrus flavor create a delightful profile. The Allsick Wolf's Breath effects are praiseworthy, inducing a tingly and arousing full-bodied experience that leaves you couch-locked while your mind elevates with clarity and focus. It's a popular choice for addressing cramps, depression, and insomnia.

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Modified Grapes
attributes.body: Modified Grapes is an Indica weed strain resulting from a cross between GMO and Purple Punch. This strain is favored by experienced cannabis consumers for its beautiful purple color and its flavors reminiscent of grape, berry, and honey. According to our customers, Modified Grapes is associated with effects like drowsiness, relaxation, and arousal. Consumers often turn to Modified Grapes to alleviate symptoms related to anxiety, stress, and insomnia.

This famous cross of Cherry Pie and Girl Scout Cookies has become a traditional staple of every connoisseur’s private stash. Meant to remind you of the dessert on your most important day, this mix of sweet, tangy, and creamy flavors will have you wanting to renew your vows. With hints of strawberries and cherries, mixed with the boldness of vanilla and cream, the perfectly balanced cake flavor will bring you right to where you want to be. Wedding Cake will leave you saying: “I do”. Powered by Dime Industries hardware, this device offers 3 heat custom settings (4.2v to 3.2v), pre-heat function, easy air flow, and is USB-C rechargeable. Get ready for a munchie-inducing experience where the only dilemma is choosing between another hit or raiding the pantry for actual cookies

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Blue Dream
attributes.body: Blue Dream is a popular Sativa cannabis strain, a cross between Blueberry and Haze. Known for its balanced effects, it has a sweet, fruity aroma with hints of berries. THC level on this strain is on the higher side, offering a gentle relaxation of the body without extreme sedation, and a creative and focused head high. Blue Dream is favored for its potential therapeutic benefits across a whole spectrum of ailments, addressing conditions like stress, anxiety, and chronic pain.

attributes.body: Orange Punch is a Sativa cannabis strain known for its extremely citrusy aroma and flavor, reminiscent of oranges. Our particular Orange Punch is a cross between Purple Punch and Mandarin Cookies. It delivers balanced effects despite being a sativa, providing calm relaxation and euphoria in both the body and the mind. Our customers have reported some therapeutic benefits, including stress relief and mood enhancement.

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Green Crack
attributes.body: Green Crack is a potent sativa-dominant strain, being a late 90s skunk varietal with razor sharp citrus aromas and flavors. It's known for providing an uplifting and energizing high. Customers report increased focus, creativity, so it is perfect for daytime use. Some find therapeutic benefits for managing stress and fatigue.

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Lemon Skunk
attributes.body: Lemon Skunk is a Sativa Strain with a citrusy/skunky "Punch You In The Face" aroma and balanced effects. Lemon Skunk has dense, trichome-covered buds with vibrant green and orange hues with a higher than average THC content. Lemon Skunk is effective for people with Depression, Stress, and Nausea, with none of the energy that comes from your usual sativa.

attributes.name: KPUFF PLATINUM KLEAR 1GM San Fernando Valley Hybrid
Enchanted Botanicals - Peach Crescendo
attributes.body: Peach Crescendo, a cross between Peach Rings and Crescendo, is a hybrid strain known for its citrusy tropical flavor, sweet peach exhale, and notes of spice. Peach Crescendo's effects are bar none, it has a full body calming effect that leaves you couch-locked while your mind elevates with clarity and focus. Despite the deep physical relaxation however, your mental energy remains unaffected. It's a popular choice for addressing insomnia, appetite loss, chronic pain, and muscle spasms. Peach Crescendo is great for customers experiencing many types of pain and great for cramps!

attributes.name: Calm
attributes.body: Enjoy a delicious fusion of flavors! The soothing lavender undertones combine seamlessly with the sweet and exotic lychee taste, resulting in a delectable, calming profile. In summary, the 4:1 CBN|THC lavender lychee cannabis gummy is a visually stunning and soothing edible formulated to encourage relaxation and potential sleep support. With its unique blend of cannabinoids, delightful flavor, and potential calming effects, it offers a delightful solution for those seeking a peaceful and tranquil experience.

attributes.name: Sleep
attributes.body: Once you taste this gummy, you'll experience a burst of wild berry flavor that's delicious and mouthwatering. It contains an equal amount of CBG and CBN and is complemented by a moderate amount of THC. This cannabinoid combination is designed to promote relaxation, reduce anxiety, and enhance sleep. CBG may provide mild euphoria, while CBN is known for its sedative effects, making it ideal for those seeking help with sleep, as well as melatonin.

attributes.name: Energy
attributes.body: ENERGY is a flavorful and balanced gummy that combines the best of both CBD and THC, offering potential therapeutic benefits with precise dosing. This gummy features the delightful flavors of green tea and hibiscus, which provides a refreshing and slightly tangy taste. These natural flavors complement the cannabis components, making it a delicious treat.

attributes.name: Focus
attributes.body: Upon biting into this gummy, you'll be greeted by a burst of watermelon sweetness that's both juicy and refreshing. The natural watermelon flavor pairs beautifully with the subtle, fragrant undertones of rose, creating a delightful fusion of flavors that dances on your taste buds. The gummy features a balanced 2:1 CBD/THC ratio. This means it contains twice as much CBD as THC.
